{"tid":331892,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 將推出i5 六核處理器產品，正面迎戰AMD","createTime":"2017-07-22T14:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T17:54:05.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49647827cda70ed64b95c9dfa204bd5a2ce75626","tid":331892,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Intel計劃推出多款Coffee Lake處理器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/coffee-lake-x-1000x563-750x422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fcoffee-lake-x-1000x563-750x422.jpg&h=d8e375a5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nCore i7 8700（K）<br />\n幾個月內Intel將推出採用Coffee Lake架構的新型六核處理器。據報導高階i7 8700K處理器的頻率為3.7 GHz。與最近推出的Core i9 7800X相比，i7-8700K的TDP比較低只有95W（對上140W）。這無疑會影響i9-7800X的銷售。Intel還推出了i7 8700非K，據說是以3.2 GHz頻率運行。<br />\n<br />\nCore i5也有6核？<br />\n謠言中最有趣的部分是i5系列的6核處理器。與i7相比的主要區別是缺乏Hyperthreading。i5-8600K處理器的頻率為3.6 GHz，與i7-8700K（95W）的TDP相同。根據CPC Hardware表示六核系列不會在8600K結束。核心時脈為2.8 GHz，TDP為65W的Core i5-8400據稱是最慢的6核桌上型處理器CPU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。這是對AMD的Ryzen 5的直接回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 6核Mobile處理器<br />\nIntel也將推出純Mobile 6核CPU。與桌上型版本相比，Coffee Lake Mobile的TDP在45W時具有更低的時脈速度（〜2.0 GHz）。該報告最後以Coffee Lake U四核處理器為結尾，與有令人印象深刻的28W TDP。這是Intel U系列（低功耗筆記型電腦）的第一款四核CPU。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/intel/38250/intel%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%BE%E5%85%AD%E6%A0%B8coffee-lake%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fintel%2F38250%2Fintel%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%25A0%25B8coffee-lake%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&d=ZM0jouo7Vlg%2BeAAmEV3FLdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=622a9219\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/intel/38250/intel%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%BE%E5%85%AD%E6%A0%B8coffee-lake%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8/</a>"},{"pid":"fff57b48999a4ac6834e802bca841c3206c50ef7","tid":331892,"uid":71728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"Win 10 之前俾google工程師爆左個用多核cpu 會lag到仆街既bug解決左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9ff3a642774c7c08465ceb18ff024a1e24ce4f","tid":331892,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:08:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">疑是 INTEL 第 8 代 COFFEE LAKE 處理器 CPU-Z 資訊</div><br />\n<br />\n於 Ptt 電蝦版上 chrisdar 玩家貼出疑是 Intel 第 8 代 Coffee Lake 處理器 CPU-Z 資訊。<br />\n<br />\n此處理器 TDP 80W，應屬於非超頻的 i7-8700 處理器資訊，有著 6 核心 12 執行緒，運行於 3.9GHz，但應該能自動超至 4.3GHz，另有著 12MB 的 L3 快取。<br />\n<br />\n支援指令集請參考下圖。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SsnPhrm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FSsnPhrm.png&h=855f5dbe&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/intel/38498/intel-8-coffee-lake-8700/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fintel%2F38498%2Fintel-8-coffee-lake-8700%2F&d=ZM0jouo7Vlg%2BeAAmEV3FLdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5ecfba9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/intel/38498/intel-8-coffee-lake-8700/</a>"},{"pid":"777fe008958e05e85282d5d8efed6b5aaaa876a7","tid":331892,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\">疑是 INTEL 第 8 代 COFFEE LAKE 處理器 CPU-Z 資訊</div><br />\n<br />\n於 Ptt 電蝦版上 chrisdar 玩家貼出疑是 Intel 第 8 代 Coffee Lake 處理器 CPU-Z 資訊。<br />\n<br />\n此處理器 TDP 80W，應屬於非超頻的 i7-8700 處理器資訊，有著 6 核心 12 執行緒，運行於 3.9GHz，但應該能自動超至 4.3GHz，另有著 12MB 的 L3 快取。<br />\n<br />\n支援指令集請參考下圖。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/SsnPhrm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FSsnPhrm.png&h=855f5dbe&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/intel/38498/intel-8-coffee-lake-8700/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fintel%2F38498%2Fintel-8-coffee-lake-8700%2F&d=ZM0jouo7Vlg%2BeAAmEV3FLdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5ecfba9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/intel/38498/intel-8-coffee-lake-8700/</a></blockquote><br />\n我估8700k all core turbo 3.9-4.0ghz"},{"pid":"c91c24eab18a0a540a39f74d44a193bbfe8e0687","tid":331892,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Win 10 之前俾google工程師爆左個用多核cpu 會lag到仆街既bug解決左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSource?"},{"pid":"bacfd1340b73fc6897b9d279cc7badec8bd2640d","tid":331892,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Win 10 之前俾google工程師爆左個用多核cpu 會lag到仆街既bug解決左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSource?</blockquote><br />\n好似2x核先會"},{"pid":"11a073efcea898b6ab3dd845122852af2bdbc012","tid":331892,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Win 10 之前俾google工程師爆左個用多核cpu 會lag到仆街既bug解決左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSource?</blockquote><br />\n好似2x核先會</blockquote><br />\n該問題在 CPU 核心數越多，關閉和開啟的動作越頻繁的情況下，窒機就越嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" c